der.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><p>Restructuring bank and ABL facilities of £120m for a borrower client.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><p>Borrower side for £13m refinance for veterinary group.</p><p>‍</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"section_testimonial\"><div class=\"w-embed\"><style>\n.section_testimonial:has(.w-dyn-empty) {\n  display: none;\n}\n</style></div><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"divider-horizontal\"></div><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div fs-slider-type=\"cms\" fs-slider-instance=\"fs-1-card-slider\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_instance\"><div class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation-wrapper\"><div class=\"testimonial_icon-wrapper\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/assets/69010fb7542aa2ee07e42406_quote-2.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"testimonial_icon\"></div><div fs-slider-element=\"navigation\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation\"><button fs-slider-element=\"previous\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M14.71 15.88L10.83 12l3.88-3.88a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41-1.41L8.71 11.3a.996.996 0 0 0 0 1.41l4.59 4.59c.39.39 1.02.39 1.41 0c.38-.39.39-1.03 0-1.42\"></path></svg></div></button><button fs-slider-element=\"next\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M9.29 15.88L13.17 12L9.29 8.12a.996.996 0 1 1 1.41-1.41l4.59 4.59c.39.39.39 1.02 0 1.41L10.7 17.3a.996.996 0 0 1-1.41 0c-.38-.39-.39-1.03 0-1.42\"></path></svg></div></button></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"list-wrapper\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div fs-slider-element=\"list\" role=\"list\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list w-dyn-items\"><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I was impressed by the team at Black Solicitors LLP. Every member of staff I dealt with was pleasant and professional, demonstrating a clear commitment to helping me rather than just driving up costs.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">My first time using Moonstone, I&#x27;ve used a few solicitors over time, working with team at Moonstone has been effortless and efficient, I would be happy to recommend and use again.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">It’s clear that client care and hospitality are taken seriously here. I would highly recommend Moonstone to anyone looking for a professional, welcoming and experienced legal firm.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Very impressed with their experience from start to finish. The legal team were exceptionally friendly, welcoming, and professional throughout. The security staff were particularly polite and approachable, making visitors feel comfortable as soon as they arrived. </div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Great communication, understanding, support, Knowledge. We keep coming back as well trusted.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Very professional, excellent communication and seamless and quick service...Highly Recommended. Thank you!</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Very prompt friendly service - Moonstone Advocates get things completed rapidly and smoothly, friendly staff.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Would highly recommend - they handled our sale with great professionalism and patience. They responded to any request within a timely manner.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div element-reveal=\"trigger\" class=\"section_team\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"slider-main_component\"><div fs-slider-type=\"cms\" fs-slider-instance=\"fs-4-card-slider\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_instance\"><h2 data-scroll-speed=\"0.025\" data-scroll=\"\" class=\"heading-style-h2\">Experts in every area</h2><div fs-slider-element=\"list-wrapper\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div fs-slider-element=\"list\" role=\"list\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_list w-dyn-items\"><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div hover-zoom=\"trigger\" class=\"team-member_item\"><a href=\"/our-people/talah-hussain\" class=\"team-member_item w-inline-block\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"team-member_image-wrapper\"><img hover-zoom=\"target\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b44ab164a8844c96471e18/6a1ef9bcfeeeb09f9de78e59_695d1bfdbe427f9a20fd700a_Moonstone-JMA-PHOTOGRAPHY-DSC_5447%2520-low-res.jpeg\" class=\"image is-team\"></div></div>